author: The Wall Street Journal
description:
President Biden attended Jimmy Carter’s funeral along with all four living former presidents—Bill Clinton, Barack Obama, George W. Bush and President-elect Donald Trump. Vice President Kamala Harris and former Vice Presidents Al Gore and Mike Pence were also at the service at the Washington National Cathedral.

title: Watch: Trump, Biden, Obama and Others Enter Jimmy Carter’s Funeral
